  <h2 id="ethics">Keep it obviously fictional</h2>
  <p>
    These formats are funny <strong>because everyone knows they're jokes</strong>. Keep it that way: don't use fake chats to impersonate real people, fabricate evidence, spread misinformation or harass anyone — that can be illegal, not just uncool. If you're posting something that could be mistaken for a real conversation, label it as a mockup. Fake chats as content = great. Fake chats passed off as real receipts = how you get banned everywhere.
  </p>

